    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit features a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed cooling system to ensure thermal efficiency during spirited driving. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional traction and corner-exit rotation. The chassis is supported by upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for precise turn-in and minimal body roll. While the finish shows minor road rash, the powertrain and drivetrain remain robust, offering a visceral, analog performance experience.",
