      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and serves as a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver. The exterior retains its deep luster with only minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned and show minimal bolstering wear, while every electronic feature functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is sound, benefiting from a comprehensive service history, including a recent fluid flush and brake inspection. It drives tight and true, offering a smooth yet responsive experience that reflects its history of preventative maintenance. This is a turn-key car ready for its next owner who values both reliability and presentation.",
