      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next adventure! I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions. Can\u2019t wait to see it go to a great new home!",
