      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 straight-six. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, equipped with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical subframe reinforcement has been completed, and the suspension bushings have been refreshed to maintain precise turn-in response. Though showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the drivetrain remains robust, providing a pure analog driving experience.",
